@startuml ai_prediction_state
!theme plain
title AI Prediction State Chart Diagram

[*] --> ImageReceived

ImageReceived --> Validating : startValidation()\n[Begin image validation]

Validating --> Valid : validationPassed()\n[Image is valid chest X-ray]
Validating --> Invalid : validationFailed()\n[Not a chest X-ray image]

Invalid --> [*] : reject()\n[Image rejected, process terminated]

Valid --> Processing : startAnalysis()\n[Begin AI cardiomegaly detection]

Processing --> AnalysisComplete : analysisFinished()\n[AI model returns result]
Processing --> ProcessingError : analysisFailed()\n[AI processing error]

ProcessingError --> Processing : retry()\n[Retry analysis]
ProcessingError --> Failed : maxRetriesExceeded()\n[Give up after max retries]

AnalysisComplete --> ResultStored : storeResult()\n[Save prediction to database]

ResultStored --> NotificationSent : notifyDoctor()\n[Notify requesting doctor]

NotificationSent --> [*] : complete()\n[Prediction process complete]

Failed --> [*] : cleanup()\n[Clean up failed prediction]

' Self-transitions
Processing --> Processing : updateProgress()\n[Update processing status]

' Notes
note right of ImageReceived
  X-ray image uploaded
  by technician
end note

note right of Validating
  Checking if image is
  valid chest X-ray
end note

note right of Valid
  Image passes validation
  Ready for AI analysis
end note

note right of Invalid
  Image rejected
  (not chest X-ray)
end note

note right of Processing
  AI model analyzing
  for cardiomegaly signs
end note

note right of AnalysisComplete
  Prediction generated
  with confidence score
end note

note right of ProcessingError
  AI analysis failed
  Retry possible
end note

note right of ResultStored
  Prediction saved
  in database
end note

note right of NotificationSent
  Doctor notified
  of available results
end note

note right of Failed
  Prediction failed
  after max retries
end note

@enduml